of a heart condition.

959
01:03:33,355 --> 01:03:36,691
Woe is us!
We're in a lot of trouble!

960
01:03:40,153 --> 01:03:45,075
So, a rich little man
with white hair died.

961
01:03:45,867 --> 01:03:48,661
What does that got to do
with the price of rice, right?

962
01:03:48,703 --> 01:03:50,747
And why is that woe to us?

963
