Because less than three percent
of you people read books.

966
01:04:04,135 --> 01:04:07,806
Because less than 15 percent of you
read newspapers.

967
01:04:07,889 --> 01:04:11,643
Because the only truth you know
is what you get over this tube.

968
01:04:11,726 --> 01:04:15,230
Right now, there is a whole
and entire generation...

969
01:04:15,313 --> 01:04:18,525
that never knew anything
that didn't come out of this tube!

970
01:04:19,734 --> 01:04:23,988
This tube is the Gospel.
The ultimate revelation.

971
01:04:24,072 --> 01:04:26,241
This tube can make or break...

972
01:04:26,324 --> 01:04:29,035
