sitting in Mr. Ruddy's office
on the 20th floor.

980
01:04:52,851 --> 01:04:57,105
And when the 12th largest company
in the world...

981
01:04:57,188 --> 01:05:00,608
controls the most awesome,
goddamn propaganda force...

982
01:05:00,692 --> 01:05:02,610
in the whole godless world...

983
01:05:02,694 --> 01:05:06,740
