for truth on this network!

984
01:05:06,823 --> 01:05:09,826
So you listen to me.
Listen to me!

985
01:05:09,909 --> 01:05:12,662
Television is not the truth.

986
01:05:12,746 --> 01:05:15,248
Television's
a goddamned amusement park!

987
01:05:15,290 --> 01:05:19,544
Television is a circus, a carnival,
a traveling troupe of acrobats...

988
01:05:19,627 --> 01:05:23,214
storytellers, dancers, singers,
jugglers, sideshow freaks...

989
01:05:23,298 --> 01:05:26,134
lion tamers and football players.

990
01:05:26,176 --> 01:05:28,636
We're in the boredom-killing business.

991
01:05:30,680 --> 01:05:34,684
So if you want the truth,
go to God.

992
01:05:34,768 --> 01:05:37,145
Go to your gurus.

993
01:05:37,228 --> 01:05:39,272
Go to yourselves!

994
01:05:39,314 --> 01:05:43,443
Because that's the only place
you're ever gonna find any real truth.

995
01:05:44,819 --> 01:05:48,948
But, man, you're never gonna get
any truth from us.

996
01:05:49,032 --> 01:05:51,951
We'll tell you anything you wanna hear.
We lie like hell.

997
01:05:51,993 --> 01:05:55,038
We'll tell you that Kojak
always gets the killer...

998
01:05:55,121 --> 01:05:58,333
and that nobody ever gets cancer
in Archie Bunker's house.

999
01:05:58,416 --> 01:06:00,752
And no matter how much trouble
the hero is in, don't worry.

1000
01:06:00,835 --> 01:06:03,546
Look at your watch.
At the end of the hour he'll win!

1001
01:06:03,630 --> 01:06:07,092
We'll tell you any shit
you want to hear!

1002
01:06:07,175 --> 01:06:10,929
We deal in illusions.
None of it is true!

1003
01:06:11,012 --> 01:06:14,974
But you people sit there,
day after day, night after night.

1004
01:06:15,058 --> 01:06:19,229
You're all ages, colors, creeds.
We're all you know.

1005
01:06:19,312 --> 01:06:22,232
You're beginning to believe
the illusions we're spinning here.

1006
01:06:22,315 --> 01:06:26,111
You're beginning to think the tube is
reality and your own lives are unreal.

1007
01:06:26,194 --> 01:06:28,279
You do whatever the tube tells you!

1008
01:06:28,363 --> 01:06:30,490
You dress like the tube,
eat like the tube...

1009
01:06:30,573 --> 01:06:33,702
raise your children like the tube,
even think like the tube.

1010
01:06:33,785 --> 01:06:37,330
This is mass madness, you maniacs!

1011
01:06:37,372 --> 01:06:40,125
In God's name, you people
are the real thing!

1012
01:06:40,208 --> 01:06:42,377
We are the illusion!

1013
01:06:42,460 --> 01:06:47,257
So turn off your television sets.
Turn them off right now.

1014
01:06:47,340 --> 01:06:49,342
Turn them off and leave them off.

1015
01:06:49,384 --> 01:06:52,595
Turn them off in the middle
of this sentence.

1016
01:06:52,679 --> 01:06:54,681
Turn them off!

1017
01:07:09,112 --> 01:07:11,990
UBS was running at a cash flow
of break-even point...

1018
